⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Scarlet Rot
node ER · ER · ⟦The Scarlet Rot:ER:2fc5aa⟧

WHO   — The Scarlet Rot — the bloom that devours from within
WHAT  — The power of an Outer God of decay and rebirth — a crimson corruption that blooms through flesh and land alike.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the lake of rot beneath the earth; flesh and land wherever the bloom takes hold  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It stands as a rival order — decay as another kind of cycle, not framed as simple evil.
HOW   — It spreads as living rot, flowering into grotesque beauty through whatever it touches, body or soil.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  What withers is not ending — the rot only blooms what the world refuses to bury.

